Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=4}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's smartphone?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.40,0:00:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I need you to locate her. {Hey, Arona. Find my Hoshino}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.38,0:00:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried accessing the GSC's central network,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't identify her location.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can find some clue.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.98,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.63,0:00:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.72,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.43,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Is that you, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? {uwu?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.83,0:02:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be the right floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you, {*}Mr. Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.35,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long been eager to\ndiscuss matters directly with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As the GSC President's enigmatic guest,\nyour reputation precedes you,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.20,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher of the Federal Investigations Club Schale.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be so on guard. {BE NOT AFRAID}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not looking to become your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we much prefer the opposite.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.48,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of a tiny school such as Abydos\nis of little consequence to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you—you're a different matter entirely.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold the potential to become\na formidable threat to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Where are my manners?\nAllow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.09,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Black Suit. I won't mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown rather fond of this name, you see?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We are much like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our origins also lie outside of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.87,0:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What separates us is that we simply hail\nfrom a different realm than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.43,0:04:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gematria.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our name.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it into your terms,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.94,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the organisation to which I belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.07,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission lies in expanding knowledge\nthrough observation, exploration, and experimentation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.26,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Through that lens, you may consider us enigmatic beings,\nnot too dissimilar from yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But onto the main topic.\nIf I might venture to ask,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would you be interested\nin entering a partnership with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You would reject an opportunity\nto unearth the truth behind the mystical?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If not Kivotos's Mystics,\nwhat, then, {\i1}are{\i0} you pursuing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All I care about is getting Hoshino back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.45,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what, pray tell, grants you\nthe authority to make such a demand?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.67,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} is no longer a student at Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you haven't overlooked\nthe form submitted by your own student?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I saw her withdrawal form.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what else is there to argue?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She no longer falls under your purview.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't signed that form yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's still part of the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still the vice president of Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's still my precious student.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.93,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're their teacher,\nany significant{### /drastic?} actions necessitate your signature.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather inconvenient.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You deceived my students. \NYou and your organisation.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You toyed with their feelings\nand took advantage of their suffering.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.92,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of "good" or "evil", our actions\nwould unambiguously fall under "evil".
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil, yes, but well within our rights.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would do ill to suggest otherwise.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.67,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,ED,The disaster that struck Abydos was not our doing. {Transition with "And" here, I think --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.06,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandstorms that besieged Abydos were atypical,\nbut not outside the realm of possibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Natural disasters are always unpredictable.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Should some people suffer of thirst as a result,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunists will naturally emerge to sell them water.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is simply business as usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that water is sold at an exorbitant price?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly a rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Such scenarios are commonplace in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.84,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who possess exploit those who lack.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Determining one's future is a luxury\nthe weak aren't afforded.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Schale's teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.18,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san}, and in return,\nI'll guarantee Abydos's well-being.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.56,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture a world where they\ncan attend school without fear.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} would want, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.11,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that were possible,\nthey wouldn't want this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.75,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that no matter my efforts,\nyou will continue to oppose us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are powerless.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack any means of fighting us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.31,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone needs my help,\nI refuse to idly stand by.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to prove to them
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.53,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that no matter how bad things get, as long as they\ndon't give up, their voices will reach {\i1}someone{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simply absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are those girls still alone then?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, their voices reached {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just walk away?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their problem. It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, why, {\i1}why{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why do you refuse?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.02,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls were in pain this entire time,\nand not a single adult took responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're saying {\i1}you{\i0} will take responsibility?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.69,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not your children.\nWhy put the onus on yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not my children.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, a letter brought me to Abydos
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just so happened to meet them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a stranger to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does that matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are crying for help!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you need?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.51,0:09:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you believe that's how adults take responsibility? {Oooooof, the intro sequence is back to haunt us. I'm not in love with this, but }
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,ED/QC,If they laugh, you join them. {"join" feels like it's missing too much context here. Maybe "you share their joy".}{### still kinda prefer what we have now, but I want petzku's opinion for these few lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,ED/QC,If they're sad, you console them. {"If they're sad, you dry their tears."}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,ED/QC,If they're lost, you guide them{ home --ik}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be an adult!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you couldn't be more wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults bend society to their own will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.75,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They decide what is right, what is proper.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the norm, and what is not.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults rule the aimless with authority, {"aimless" feels off. The original is "they use authority to rule those without authority", so there should be a clear parallel between the ideas. Maybe "The masses kneel before their authority, the ignorant bow before their knowledge, and the weak cower before their strength." --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the ignorant with knowledge,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the weak with power.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is what it means to be an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply don't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.34,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have ruled over Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been yours.\nThe authority, the privileges...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mystics that fill this academy city. {### petz, does this sentence fragment need to be capitalised?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.38,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been brief,\nbut you held it all in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you threw it all away\nwithout a moment's hesitation!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth and mystery. Authority. Riches. {\i1}Power{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To throw that all away is madness.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I told you, you would never understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears we've reached an impasse.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.23,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had high hopes for you, but I'm afraid\nI'll have to cut our negotiations short.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.46,0:10:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} in the laboratory\nbeneath one of Kaiser PMC's desert bases.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.39,0:10:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Via Mimesis we were able to observe\na different facet of Mystics: Terror.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.43,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal was to to explore\nits application on a living student.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.71,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl was meant to serve\nas a test bed to confirm our hypotheses.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hypotheses?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.69,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that negotiations have broken down,\nmy hands are tied.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate, but our involvement ends here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Hoshino is...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Do what you will.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to take her, if you'd so like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.12,0:11:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, assuming the director\nallows you to see her in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we had this conversation.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,May we meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A laboratory underneath the Kaiser PMC base...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they've been holding her captive?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't go in without a plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we even say once we find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, before that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We scold her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back on her word.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She deserves to be punished.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So we scold her
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for her own good.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.73,0:12:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,TL,Let's find her together and say "welcome home". {So there are two ways of handling this line. One is to wrangle the "tadaima" into a way that makes sense in English, and then use the same phrasing for the finale of Vol1 Chapter2. The other is to rewrite that entire scene to say something a bit different. I might gravitate towards the second bit, just to make my own life easier. --ik}{### wfm, will leave it to you}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where did {\i1}that{\i0} corny line come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too sappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It just {\i1}screams{\i0} blue skies and happy memories! {Need... blue archive... pun... Tried looking at the OST names for inspiration but idk how well it works --ik}{### sorry dude aint got anything}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We could never pull that off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,even if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll say it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.46,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't catch me dead saying that!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nonomi laugh}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but there's only five of us—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't win on our own.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to find some allies.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about PS68?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They did help us before, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone. It's been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well, Hifumi{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! It was all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.54,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to visit your school, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it, where's Hoshino{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, thing is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed a lot\nsince we last saw each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.43,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wish we'd known sooner\nwhat Hoshino{**-senpai} was going through.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could have stopped her.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're here about Hoshino{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. To put it simply,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd like Trinity's help to save Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.41,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask for your help, {*}Miss Nagisa{*Nagisa-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I try first?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.59,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This shortcake is rich with cream\nand complements the tea exquisitely.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this Mont Blanc is equally irresistible.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, {*}Miss Nagisa{*Nagisa-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.81,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those students from Abydos have helped me before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So please—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.40,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would indeed appear that this company,\nKaiser PMC, is a negative influence on our students.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'll hel—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the matter of the Treaty to consider.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to act hastily.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have some time to think this over?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,QC,So we're put on hold, huh? {no hyphen here, but I also don't know if this call center metaphor works. Maybe "couldn't even get an answer, huh" --ik} {### petz, thoughts?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this was my idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding help is a lot tougher than we thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.36,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the next group helping us either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still no reason to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.62,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that the others couldn't attend this meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked for Chinatsu{**-san} to attend at least,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but this school has a bit of trouble following the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Chinatsu{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for being late.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's mine...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.53,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for keeping you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We just managed to finish up—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your break!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's trouble in the cafeteria! {## FUUKA IS BEING KIDNAPPED AGAIN (눈‸눈 )}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,TLC,Thank you. {specifically, thank you for the tea. Just "thank you" feels a bit out of the blue. Thank you for coming? Thank you for waiting? Thank you for letting me leave? --ik}{### obvious enough from just looking at the video imo}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for all the confusion!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are things always this hectic around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's actually been on the quiet side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, I wonder how\nthe negotiations are going on their end?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Head Prefect is busy right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not available. Come back later.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must talk to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get on your knees and lick my feet, maybe I can—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.33,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you have zero pride as an adult?\nShouldn't you at least hesitate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really means it...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Enough! Get off me already!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him. He's on his knees.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation must be quite serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, President Hina...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.69,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not actually kneeling, he's... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking... my feet...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.62,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Prefect Team didn't give us an answer, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We did what we could! {Well, HE did what he could... the glorious bastard...}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.79,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones left are Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.09,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they agree to help us?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.46,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This one's the one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what gives?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.35,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the address they gave me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You're telling me this is the PS68 office?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a miscommunication?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.48,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only lead we have on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, we came all this way for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did they run off to?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome in!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful stall!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a nostalgic vibe!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.93,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, Shiba Seki Ramen started out as just a little stall.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I'm back in those days, almost.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.36,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can have your ramen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I don't know what woulda happened\nif it weren't for that cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would've figured something out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like quittin' was an option anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.78,0:19:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty o' folk\nwaiting to taste my ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,ED,Earlier, these two darlings stopped by. {two bonny lasses. Make him Scottish now and confuse EVERYONE --ik}{### lol I am awful at accents}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked tucked right in, said my ramen\nhit just the spot after a long day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't ask for more than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How're things for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, could be better.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We tryied reaching out to\na lot of people to ask for help.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.51,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're having some trouble\nlocating the last group.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't find them soon,\nwe may have to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, can we get the cheque?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.57,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to fight Kaiser PMC for free?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.16,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's in it for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, and I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.88,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kayoko{**-chan}. Take a close look.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.38,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.05,0:19:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"We don't need your money.\nThis super tasty ramen is all we need!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's written all over her face!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama} is so brave!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.77,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't waste time with words\nas she marches into hell for a bowl of ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.44,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the picture of a hard-boiled outlaw!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I think it over first?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.07,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.75,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Hold on, Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beat yourself up over it, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith that they'll help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faith, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.68,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, my restaurant'll always be there\nso long as my customers believe in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same thing 'ere.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.32,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If everything goes wrong,\njust start over and try again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There'll always be a path forward,\nas long as you believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go get 'em, Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And once you're done,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}come back for a bowl o' ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've packed plenty of ammunition.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser PMC doesn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the intel {*}Teacher{*Sensei} got us,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.69,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino is being held in District 51,\nin one of Kaiser PMC bases.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our objective is to rescue Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{=5}Let's do this.

